<hr class="chap x-ebookmaker-drop" aria-hidden="true">
<div class="chapter">
<p class="center fm-xl">THE BIBLE: SHOULD IT BE IN THE
SCHOOL ROOM?</p>
</div>

<hr class="chap x-ebookmaker-drop" aria-hidden="true">
<div class="chapter">
